xyz.msws.nope.modules.npc

Class NPC

  • java.lang.Object
    • xyz.msws.nope.modules.npc.NPC

  • public class NPC
extends java.lang.Object
    Easy to use object that handles the packets internally, NPCs should ideally only be sent to one player, otherwise their locations may be confusing.
    Author:
    imodm
